4 section by each district attorney's office. A copy of
5 the report shall be distributed to the Governor, the
6 President Pro Tempore of the Senate, the Speaker of
7 the House of Representatives and the chairs of the
8 Senate and House Judiciary Committees.
9 c. For purposes of this paragraph, "jailhouse informant"
10 "informant" means a person who provides, or who the
